      <title>马斯克为何涉足英国儿童性侵团伙丑闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/why-is-elon-musk-criticizing-keir-starmer-over-uk-grooming-gang-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克指责英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 参与了数十年前发生的儿童性剥削团伙丑闻，此举让英国政府陷入守势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/why-is-elon-musk-criticizing-keir-starmer-over-uk-grooming-gang-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 15:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
